1. Switch is used to declare multiple options. We can declare multiple cases but only one dfault caseis allowed.

allowed argument: byte , short , int, char, string, enum, wrapper classes.

Not allowed arguments: flot, long, double.

Switch(arg)
{
	case label: statment
		break;
	Case label: statement
		break;
		;;;;
	default : statement
		break;
}

